Interface TokenSequenceFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AllUppercaseFrenchFilter, DiacriticRemover, EmptyTokenAfterDuFilter, EmptyTokenBeforeDuquelFilter, LowercaseFilter, LowercaseFirstWordFrenchFilter, LowercaseKnownFirstWordFilter, LowercaseKnownWordFilter, QuoteNormaliser, UppercaseSeriesFilter, UpperCaseSeriesFrenchFilter

    public interface TokenSequenceFilter
    A filter for applying a given transformation to a TokenSequence. This may call token.setText(String) to any token, and add empty tokens.
